      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What happens to your data once it is on the dark web?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the past few years, given the alarming escalation of data breaches, dark web marketplaces are reportedly flooded with stolen user credentials &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/what-happens-your-data-once-it-dark-web-1617115&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/what-happens-your-data-once-it-dark-web-1617115&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The eight steps you need to take to start threat hunting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;step-by-step instructions on how to conduct a hunt.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cybereason.com/blog-the-eight-steps-to-threat-hunting/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.cybereason.com/blog-the-eight-steps-to-threat-hunting/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What happens to your data once it is on the dark web?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cybercriminals are known to use stolen credentials to launch cybercrime campaigns as well as perpetuate crimes such as identity theft and scams.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/what-happens-your-data-once-it-dark-web-1617115&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/what-happens-your-data-once-it-dark-web-1617115&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Researchers find data breaches more likely at large teaching hospitals&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The researchers, including Ge Bai, an assistant professor at the Johns Hopkins Carey Business School, reviewed nearly 1,800 data breaches &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.baltimoresun.com/bs-md-hospital-breaches-20170415-story.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.baltimoresun.com/bs-md-hospital-breaches-20170415-story.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
